headline: DoorDash : Further Support for Los Angeles Relief and Recovery Efforts
summary: As of Friday afternoon, historic wildfires have devastated Los Angeles County neighborhoods and forced more than 150,000 people to evacuate. Our hearts go out to everyone affected by these fires....
